Well I set the date, and I've delivered on time.
Here's de_grim, a jungle complex under attack from Terrorist forces,
The out come for the Counter Terrorists looks grim.

Swamp birds and thunder drown out the noise of foot steps trough the muddy banks and under grove. Dense fog obstructs snipers, while ferns and reeds provide limited cover for assaulters.
Rain and cloud cover provide the atmosphere for this eerie setting.

This is the map de_greensleeves. ------------------------------------------------------------------------ Terrorists have been using an abandoned castle to secretly manufacture alcohol and narcotics to sell to the public. Police have become aware of this illegal activity and plan to move in using a crack force of the worlds best poilce teams. The terrorists discover the police's plan and have no option but to try and blow up all the evidence left by their scheme. ------------------------------------------------------------------------ The map has been in developement for close to 2 years and i finally feel its finished enough to release. Its been a project that i have started and stopped many times and it has frustrated me hugely at times, so its a huge relief to finally get it out there and for people to enjoy. -The map has 64 spawnpoints but i recommend up to 32. -It has colorcorrection and hdr so make sure those options are turned on in your graphics settings. -The map has a rather large easter egg, with a custom song made for me by my very good friend Sam 'kulture' Dickison. check out his music here: www.myspace.com/kulture_uk So a big thanks to him for taking the time to add a little GMT. Also want to say a big thanks to Nath and all those who encouraged and played/ commented on the map as it was made. Wouldnt be in this state without you guys so thanks. ----------------------------------------------------------------------- Lastly thanks to anyone who presses the download button; ive spent a lot of time and energy making this so you are the guys who make it worth it. If anyone adds this to a servers rotation or wants me to tell them where the easter egg is PM me. Thanks again.

DE_GREENE by Dark Nova Studios (DNvCross and DNvLasrever) & Ted "cashed" McIlwain (released June 2010)

This map could be named de_prodigy2 for multiple reasons:

- First and foremost, because it recreates the ambiance of the official map, using most of the graphical elements (models, textures) of de_prodigy.

- Next, because the layout follows the great tradition of military bases: nice and efficient in term of gameplay but totally incoherent if you think a little about it.

- And finally because it subtly starts where de_prodigy ends.

The idea is not to take the official maps and extends it, but to let us play in the another area of this famous military map, with just a glimpse of some of the well-known location of the original map.

As usual with those mappers, the map is remarkably well done. If you really want to nitpick, you could say that some light points are a bit odd in some of the hallways...

But that's a tiny, little detail that surely won't blocking us from playing this map.

- from review at NetDay.be

About Playing against the Bots: Original NAV-file included in archive is not optimized and not place painted auto-gen (not fully playable). Here is a manually optimized and fully place painted NAV-file for this awesome map :-)

de_glacier by Dr. Spud
The World Renowned Blue Glacier Ski Lodge is in the final stages of renovations for the new winter season. A blizzard struck the lodge the previous morning, resulting in an unexpectedly deep snow pack. The blizzard caused a few trees to fall, and caused minor damages to the lodge's deck. However, the early snow shower guarantees the Blue Glacier Resort to open its doors earlier than any other ski resort in the country. The Blue Glacier Resort is expected to make record profit early in the season. Another rival high class ski resort, recovering from a bad previous season, may face bankruptcy with this competition. The owner of this resort has called in a squad of terrorists to attack the Blue Glacier lodge in an effort to force it to remain closed long into the season. The police caught wind of the attack just hours before it was planned to start... It's been a long time in the coming, but it's finally complete. The map is sort of a remake of my first one, de_resort. But really, this is a completely different map from the ground up. Months have been spent testing the layout to make it as solid as possible. Not to mention optimization of the graphics. It's done. Enjoy.
Features
  • 44 total spawn points
  • Overview radar
  • Place names
  • NAV file
  • All files zipped to bsp
  • And more snowboards than you can count
All custom content is made by Dr. Spud and may not be re-used.
